Changelog for castlehps
=======================

1.0.11 (unreleased)
------------------

- Another CORS fix


1.0.10 (2016-08-22)
------------------

- fix CORS checking

1.0.9 (2016-08-01)
------------------

- strip out images from default search results

1.0.8 (2016-07-12)
------------------

- fix portal_type query to handle multiple values in an OR query

1.0.7 (2016-07-02)
------------------

- switch to using web module so we get some web application goodies for free
  like 404, 500 messages

1.0.6 (2016-06-22)
------------------

- be able to search crawled sites

1.0.5 (2016-06-22)
------------------

- support for portal_type
- better SearchableText query

1.0.4 (2016-06-20)
------------------

- Upgrade to use latest scoring script
  [vangheem]

1.0.3 (2016-06-20)
------------------

- add loglevel configuration for sentry reporting
- adjust log level of some messages


1.0.2 (2016-06-06)
------------------

- fix missing object for accessing sentry dsn


1.0.1 (2016-06-06)
------------------

- changed underscore to hyphen for sentry related command line parameters to
  keep consistent with others


1.0.0 (2016-06-06)
------------------

- initial release, forked from client specific python 2.x/3.x service
